{
  "stem": "9665.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I can do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother, who was my partner before the war, was in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my family was in Curacao.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister and brother-in-law were in Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I had them all over the world, and I was standing there by myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother sent me some teeth, because he thought that's a good line to sell in Holland, which I appreciated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents and sister, from Curacao sent me shoes and clothing to sell in Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all this went to the reception room of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't think of the president there, in [NON-ENGLISH] in the Hague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not the teeth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know what I did with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I-- as far as I remember, I didn't sell them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the men, who was in charge there, one of them lives in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I gave them all this, because we got these people coming from Auschwitz, Bergen-Belsen, and so on, because we are talking of months and months later.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the beginning, when I gave them the cigarettes-- there was one particular instance, which I'd like to mention.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was this man who came back by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Calfus-- ?] not [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Calfus. ?] No, that's wrong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I can't think of his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, there was this man who came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- was his name [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Calfus? ?] It wasn't [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Calfus. ?] Anyway, he came back, and he said, I've lost my wife and all the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, you didn't lose your wife and all the children, because some of them are in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I had a [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Benford ?] 1,500 weight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was traveling wherever I could with this not pleasant captain, who, by that time, he was a colonel, or lieutenant colonel.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
